title: The Flash - No Way Home For The DCU?
description:
So the first proper trailer for The Flash, starring Ezra Miller and Michael Keaton dropped last night. What does this mean for James Gunn's DCU, and can a movie with this much baggage possibly succeed? Let's take a look.
